The paper deals with multi-robot motion planning, which is a subfield of robotics (cs.RO). The use of Conflict-based search (CBS) and Sampling-based Motion planning are both techniques commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and control systems (cs.SY). The paper also mentions the use of machine learning (cs.LG) and computer vision (cs.CV) in some of the experiments.
